wiki.content: Lucas Secon., who co-wrote the song told HitQuarters.com the song wasn’t specifically written for Kylie: “We had four different artists who wanted to cut it as their first singles. It wasn’t aimed specifically at her. It was just a good dance record, but obviously, it fitted into what she wanted to do. I just do tracks and whatever happens to fit, fits.” (Source Get Outta My Way Songfacts.)
